:::Jetstorm/Sharpedge/The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare:::

::Jetstorm dodges the optic blasts, but the laser blasts hit his chest.  He 
dodges the dark flame rocket, but Gets hit by the dark heat blasts. He fired 
18 rapid fire optic blasts at Nemises Enforcer, 25 energy blasts at Dark One, 
25 at Astral, and 25 at Fenox.  Sharpedge shoots the grenades to destroy 
them, but only one is destroyed.  The other one hit his foot, and destroyed 
it.  he gets hit in the leg by the gatling guns.  Now limping, he fires 2 
missles up at Scattershot, and 2 at Recklessa::
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
::The Destrocons, Falcon, and Snare hear Cerberus' words::
Skywarp: Great, another leader.
Ramjet: Hmm, I wonder what Shredders gonna say about this...
